## Description {#details}

This file contains signature information for runtime libcalls.

CodeGen uses external symbols, which it refers to by name. The <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/webassembly">WebAssembly</a> target needs type information for all functions. This file contains a big table providing type signatures for all runtime library functions that LLVM uses.
